Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《边桥谜案》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Previously on The Bridge..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事都变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A lot of things changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔玛走了  我的几个女儿也走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alma's gone, my daughters are gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斯也死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gus is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你的心情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想宰了戴维·泰特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to kill David Tate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他夺走了我的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He took everything from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克罗斯警探  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Detective Cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的新娘不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My bride is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找一个最后出现在华瑞兹的失踪女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm looking for a missing girl, last seen in Juarez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你们找的那个女孩  伊娃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我看到她在警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}一个警察把她带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}她在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那家伙打了一顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You beat that man up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是警察  不能这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a cop. You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们找到伊娃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We found Eva, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被带去了一个派对  下药  强奸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was taken to a party, drugged, raped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得揭发他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个老人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some old lady dies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守着巨款去世啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}babysitting a cartel fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此  还有一半是欧元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's not all. Half of it's euros.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}钱给你了\N米莉·昆塔纳是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"米莉·昆塔纳是谁"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Who is Millie Quintana?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}埃琳娜给我打电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}丹妮拉出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}她没下公共汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是谁画的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who did those drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆·多布斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jim Dobbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像是孩子画的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It looks like they were made by a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了我姐姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He killed my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}杀你儿子的那个畜生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}只要你说话  我马上去办  马可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我会为你宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我想亲手宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}建造属于你的山脊\N海量供选\N请致电奇普·迪亚兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  奇普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Howdy, Chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}边桥谜案\N第二季第一集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑娅·克罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sonya Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}趴下  趴在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}住手  快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}住手  这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}是我  蠢货  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}他去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那个混蛋去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}在那间房里的人  去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}一切都还好吧  老大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你找到毒品了吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不  什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿韦拉多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Abelardo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Como estas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿韦拉多  这是乔·麦肯齐和里瓦斯探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Abelardo, this is Joe McKenzie and Agent Rivas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是缉毒局的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're with the DEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平塔多先生是我们最厉害的检察官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Senor Pintado is one of our finest prosecutors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继续谈备忘录中概述的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to get back to the Condor surveillance program
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神鹰监督计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}outlined in my memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没看过你的备忘录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't read your memo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来总结一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you summarize?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  我们要恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Firstly, we'd like to congratulate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥新成立的民选政府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the new democratically elected government of Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也恭喜你升职  吉列尔莫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that goes for your promotion, too, Guillermo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Muchas gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缉毒局已做好准备  在政府允许的范围内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, the DEA stand ready to help in any way
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从各方面对你方予以协助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that the administration will allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我方全部探员被遣返的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're just not clear how we're supposed to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道该如何开展合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when all of our agents keep getting sent back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神鹰计划是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, what Condor proposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的心意我们领了  乔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We understand your concern, Joe,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们想用其他方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we prefer a different approach
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持好社会秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to achieve peace on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了跟贩毒集团休战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Short of calling a truce with the cartels
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是加派人手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or putting more boots on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你们还能怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know how you're going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-任人唯贤  -是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- With competent men in the right positions. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像阿韦拉多这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Men like Abelardo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是奇瓦瓦州新上任的检察官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's our newly appointed prosecutor to the State of Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-长官  -我正在跟我们的美国朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sir... - Now, I was just explaining our strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释针对华瑞兹市的策略\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in Juárez to our American friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这项政策包括除掉福斯托·加尔文吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does this strategy include taking out Fausto Galvan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击有组织犯罪  我们得先处理好自己的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To fight organized crime, we need to clean our own house first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉列尔莫  这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Guillermo, we have $10 million
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用了三年  花费了一千万美金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and three years invested in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想就这么完了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you pulling the plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有情报想跟我们分享\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you have any intel you want to share,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm willing to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这话什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What exactly does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要找我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't call us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会找你们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你外套上的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件外套不是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not my jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁的  反正现在穿的人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, whoever's jacket it is, you're wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是杰克·多布斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Jack Dobbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来探视的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, so, you here to see someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探视你哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是桑娅·克罗斯  丽莎的妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Sonya Cross, Lisa's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不能抽烟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't smoke in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是她妹妹吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're really her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟医生谈过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you spoken to the doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  就问过一个护士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, no, just, just a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他快不行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He, uh, he's on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可说不准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较了解这些医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been around enough doctors to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们虽然不这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, they weren't saying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一般都这样  你懂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they were, if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我能做点什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, is there something I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如再找个医生什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like, uh... find a new doctor or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well... Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想他死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want him to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想他死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you want him to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把烟抽了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, I'm gonna smoke this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}欢迎来到美国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出示护照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来美国做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you plan to do in the U.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上有携带超过一万美元的现金吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have more than $10,000 on your person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了126美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have $126.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美国前往墨西哥华瑞兹市\N请出示护照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好让你别跟我排一条队的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were supposed to use a different line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张  我们过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Calm down. We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该排另一条队的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should've used a different line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不照我说的做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why didn't you use a different line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这排人少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your line was shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是有规矩的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have a system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次别跟我排一条队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Use a different line next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的越野车呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where's the SUV?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是混合动力汽车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hybrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色环保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's good for the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混合动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Hybrid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是油电混合汽车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Electric car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心北极熊会无家可归\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm worried about the polar bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才懒得管他妈的北极熊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I don't give a shit about polar bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看起来像个小受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to look like a pillow biter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小受  我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Pillow biter"? I-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是同性恋  我不想被当成同性恋  埃利诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gay. I don't want to look gay, Eleanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you're not gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多美国人都开混合动力汽车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Many Americans drive hybrids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很多美国人是同性恋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And many Americans are gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}奇瓦瓦州警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你还好吗  马可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}军火库
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}还有毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那房子里什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那是你没仔细找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}这种小混混长大后就会成为杀手  人贩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那为什么不把他们都抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你不该在这里  马可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}别让这帮废物的朋友找机会报复你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What should I do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带它回马厩  给它喂点吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take him up to the barn, give him some grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  伊娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的人才会破坏别人的栅栏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What kind of person cuts another man's fence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:14:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人总想不劳而获  偷拖拉机  工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're looking to steal something-- tractor, tools...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还偷起牛来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}stealing cattle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃最近怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变回老样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时好时坏  有时很久都不说一句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then better, and some days she don't talk at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有提起过自己的经历吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She ever talk about what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她准备好了自然会说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She will when she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟马可联系过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You talk to Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不回我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's not returning my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能他还需要点时间休整吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I suppose he's still sorting it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也情有可原\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Figure he got his reasons for keeping quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因为这个来找我吗  桑娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that why you come up here, Sonya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多布斯快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dobbs is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死你姐姐的人早就已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The man that killed you sister left this planet a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇见他弟弟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I met his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好离那家人远点  桑娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Be best if you steered clear of that entire family, Sonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hank!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先带她回房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take her into the house.
