Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.17,0:37:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就是她的雇主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like, whoever she's working for...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.30,0:37:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能谁有这个能耐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Someone-someone made that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.47,0:37:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.49,0:37:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.27,0:37:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本就不该来打扰的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I shouldn't have interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.80,0:37:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识你真的很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was so lovely meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.78,0:37:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.74,0:37:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.72,0:37:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要把那些亲戚找出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to find those relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.22,0:37:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}建造属于你的山脊  \N海量供选  \N请致电奇普·迪亚兹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你会废他的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought you were gonna go for his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.33,0:38:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ear was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.90,0:38:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又不听话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wasn't listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.00,0:38:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你需要  等解决掉美国佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want, we can get you a new dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.34,0:38:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以给你弄条新裙子来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}after we get the Yankee.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.00,0:38:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你出主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could give you my thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.79,0:38:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看起来体面些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}help you look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.63,0:38:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国人  不加冠词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is "Yankee," Not "The Yankee,"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.04,0:38:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要新裙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I don't need a new dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.79,0:38:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.71,0:38:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇普·迪亚兹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chip Diaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.85,0:38:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.18,0:38:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.32,0:38:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想从哪里开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where would you like to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.70,0:38:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.96,0:38:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.70,0:38:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你喜欢  我还准备了些点心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got some refreshments, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.77,0:38:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带工具吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.81,0:38:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.63,0:38:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.61,0:38:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.34,0:39:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.31,0:39:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}队长
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.42,0:39:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.01,0:39:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}法院
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.94,0:39:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}恢复自由身了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.37,0:39:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}她都没现身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.31,0:39:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}她的律师签的协议书
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.60,0:39:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}这样更好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.67,0:39:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你得帮我个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.11,0:39:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}新来的检察官到了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.94,0:39:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我看见他了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.05,0:39:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你懂的  新官上任三把火
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.59,0:39:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}他想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.93,0:39:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}所有的检察官想要的都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.93,0:39:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}打响自己的名号
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.44,0:39:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}替我照顾好他
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.06,0:39:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}给他看人事档案  回答他的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.69,0:40:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.78,0:40:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.26,0:40:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}马可·鲁伊斯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.09,0:40:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}久闻大名
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.55,0:40:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你要看档案  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.81,0:40:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.13,0:40:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你在边桥上事  我都看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.91,0:40:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}对令郎的不幸  我深表哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.41,0:40:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.54,0:40:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}抱歉这里比较乱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.54,0:40:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不是一直这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.28,0:40:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}罗伯斯队长
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.19,0:40:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}别担心  你们队长这种人我见多了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.73,0:40:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}没事的  交给我  我能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.98,0:41:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我能帮你做点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.95,0:41:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不用
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.51,0:41:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不过等我安顿下来后  想跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.66,0:41:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}等我屡清头绪以后
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.88,0:41:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我得先请示一下队长
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.56,0:41:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}应该的  应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.50,0:41:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你每件事都跟他请示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.25,0:41:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.60,0:41:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.61,0:41:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}看我是否认为他需要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.92,0:41:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}这种态度比较危险
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.33,0:41:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你到底要查什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.14,0:41:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}还不能确定
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.29,0:41:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}查到了才能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.56,0:41:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.40,0:42:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝点什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.72,0:42:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.93,0:42:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我貌似应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thinking maybe I should, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.91,0:42:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.78,0:42:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.40,0:42:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他送给你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did he, uh, give you those?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.71,0:42:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.40,0:42:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为我画的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He drew them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.85,0:42:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么把他们挂起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would you, uh, put them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.07,0:42:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I like looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.11,0:42:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.87,0:42:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.49,0:42:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.74,0:42:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.23,0:42:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.60,0:43:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定要这么做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.12,0:43:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有别的选择吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What else am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.12,0:43:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想办法偷偷的给你办个签证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm trying to get you a visa without raising too many red flags.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.19,0:43:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是临时情况  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So this will be a temporary situation, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.41,0:43:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我找到别的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Until I figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.55,0:43:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要回到你的住处怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What if they come back to your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.33,0:43:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, if they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.98,0:43:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会有好果子吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they're not gonna like what they find.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.40,0:43:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.53,0:43:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我给你添了这么多麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. I-I've been too much trouble, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.57,0:43:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.20,0:43:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要内疚  伊娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing to be sorry about, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.82,0:43:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得先跟这家伙说两句话  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I need to have a word with this guy first, all right? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.67,0:44:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.07,0:44:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的流浪狗  我想抓它  结果它逃掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dang stray dog-- I tried to catch it, but it eluded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.02,0:44:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮的柯利牧羊犬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dang good-looking collie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.26,0:44:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  伊娃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.85,0:44:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢柯利牧羊犬吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You like collies?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.95,0:44:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么喜不喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.27,0:44:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种狗不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's a good breed, generally.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.25,0:44:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好帮手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.36,0:44:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把话说清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's get something straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.16,0:44:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事上  我一点执法能力都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here in a non-law enforcement capacity, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.18,0:44:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.74,0:44:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟着我会很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She'll be safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.06,0:44:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且斯蒂文兄弟很快就回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plus Brother Steven will be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.94,0:44:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他俩心有灵犀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They have a spiritual connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.42,0:44:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我不信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I don't trust you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.31,0:44:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不信任那个疯子林德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't trust that wing nut Linder, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.27,0:44:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not as far as I could throw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.80,0:44:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里是她的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This was her idea to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.09,0:44:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查了你的老底  鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See, I ran your name, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.19,0:44:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我说说塔尔萨那事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to tell me about what happened in Tulsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.82,0:44:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-哪件事  -驾驶轻型摩托车进行人身伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Which thing? - Felony assault with a dirt bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.86,0:44:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那是被触犯了底线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it was one of those stand your ground things,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.97,0:44:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是当时恰好骑着辆雅马哈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it just happened to be on a Yamaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.53,0:44:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还磕了点冰毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Might have been some meth involved
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.97,0:44:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.00,0:45:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在嗑药吗  鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You still tweakin', Bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.46,0:45:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗心革面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not that man anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.69,0:45:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have anything else you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.50,0:45:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在牧场做些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, what do you got going on up at that ranch?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.33,0:45:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代主行事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Lord's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.93,0:45:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是避风港\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.61,0:45:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天国通路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Path.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.92,0:45:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.20,0:45:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且让她跟你走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna let her go with you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.59,0:45:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你有责任照顾好她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you're responsible for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.97,0:45:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她出了事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If anything happens to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.98,0:45:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得给我个交待  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you answer to me, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.02,0:45:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.46,0:45:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.24,0:45:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  马可\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hola, Marco.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.01,0:45:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你眼神很哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.07,0:45:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}今晚我什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.30,0:46:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那要看你今晚怎么过
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.64,0:46:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.96,0:47:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}没事  只是睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.52,0:47:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}要一起喝一杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.82,0:47:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡车司机报的警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Trucker called it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.84,0:47:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是条狗吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.85,0:47:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.68,0:47:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们得把车停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.42,0:48:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我是想先让你看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I wanted you to see what we're up against first.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.31,0:48:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是辆混合动力车  要好久才回自己停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Course, it's a hybrid, so it ain't like we can wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.47,0:48:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.06,0:48:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这他妈是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.01,0:48:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.51,0:48:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女侠出马了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.78,0:48:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计  你看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dude, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.93,0:48:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.07,0:48:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计  去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dude, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.39,0:49:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Help me.

